choices.text:
{
  "ingredients": [
    "fish fillets",
    "flour",
    "salt",
    "egg",
    "breadcrumbs",
    "oil"
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "In a shallow bowl, mix together the flour and salt.",
    "In a separate bowl, beat the egg.",
    "Dip the fish fillets in the egg, then coat with the flour mixture.",
    "Dip the fish fillets in the egg again, then coat with the breadcrumbs.",
    "Heat the oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Fry the fish fillets in the hot oil until golden brown and cooked through, about 3 minutes per side."
  ]
}
